    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 9.433333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 11.033333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "……えっ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.033333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tri-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 12.533333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 12.533333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、瑠依ちゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Morning‚ Rui-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.533333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう。今朝は随分早いんやね\nどこまでお散歩行くん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Morning. You’re up awfully early today.\nGoing on a walk somewhere?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 19.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "優、すみれ、どうして……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu‚ Sumire… why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 23.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなん瑠依ちゃんと同じ理由に決まってるやん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re obviously out here for the same reason as you‚ Rui-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "プレタポルテに行くんだよね？\nだったら、三人で行かなきゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re going to Pret-A-Porter‚ right?\nThen we have to go as a trio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.966666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 31.566666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "私達三人でTRINITYAiLEなんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Together‚ the three of us are TRINITYAiLE!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 35.7
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 36
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……そこまで言うなら、私がプレタポルテに行く理由も\n分かってるでしょ？　圧力がかかるだけじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you guessed that much‚ then I’m sure you know why\nI’m going to Pret-A-Porter. They’ll do more than intimidate us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "私と朝倉社長の関係がもしマスコミにリークされたら\n星見プロに取り返しの付かない迷惑がかかる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If my relationship with President Asakura is leaked to the media‚\nit may do irreparable damage to Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.230735911745015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 50.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "……それに、トリエルもおしまいになる\nあなた達のアイドル生命だって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And what’s more… TRINITYAiLE will be done for.\nSo will your careers as idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 56.833333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん。だから瑠依ちゃんは\n一人で移籍することに決めたんやね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mm-hm‚ mm-hm. That’s why Rui-chan\ndecided to transfer over there on your own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "そしてうちらには星見プロに残れと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And you want us to stay at Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 66.3666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ。姫野さんは私が説得する\nだから――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. I’ll convince Himeno-san to leave you alone.\nSo…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 71.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "……ふざけたこと言わんとって\nうちらのこと、バカにしてんの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t be ridiculous.\nDo you think we’re stupid or something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 74.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 76.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "違うよ優ちゃん、バカなのは瑠依ちゃんだよ！\nこんなに大バカだったなんて、見損なったよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ Yu-chan‚ Rui-chan is the stupid one!\nI had no idea you were such a stupid girl. I’ve lost faith in you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 83.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、あなた達……\n人のことを、バカバカって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you girls…\nStop calling me stupid…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 88.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "うちら、三人でアイドルの頂点に立つ――\nそういう約束やったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re going to become top idols as a trio.\nThat’s what we promised‚ remember?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 94.7333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんが抜けて、うちら二人だけで頂点に立っても\nなんの意味もない。そんなら解散した方がマシやわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you leave us‚ and the two of us reach the top without you‚\nit will be completely meaningless. I’d rather disband altogether.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 104.26666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "私達は三人でTRINITYAiLE\n瑠依ちゃんの問題は、三人の問題でしょ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The three of us are TRINITYAiLE.\nYour problems are our problems!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "どうして言ってくれないの……？\n私達に、一緒に来てって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why won’t you tell us?\nWhy won’t you say you want us to come with you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 116.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "バカ、バカ、バカバカ……\nうわああああああんっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Stupid… stupid‚ stupid!\nWahhh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 124.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "……年下の子、こんなに泣かして\nほんっと、瑠依ちゃんはバカやね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look at you‚ making this little girl cry.\nYou really are stupid‚ Rui-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 131.33333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_04-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "…………わ、私だって、一緒に来て欲しい\nそう、言いたかった……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but… in my heart‚ I want you to come with me.\nI wanted to ask you to come!",
